    "endTime": 475.759,
    "text": "coming all the way down my arms"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 475.759,
    "endTime": 477.039,
    "text": "gross"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.039,
    "endTime": 478.56,
    "text": "what do you remember"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.56,
    "endTime": 481.199,
    "text": "about your first date write it in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.199,
    "endTime": 483.039,
    "text": "comments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.039,
    "endTime": 486.639,
    "text": "now remember with the two infinitive is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.639,
    "endTime": 488.879,
    "text": "used to talk about something that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 488.879,
    "endTime": 492.4,
    "text": "someone needs to do to remind them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.4,
    "endTime": 494.08,
    "text": "to do something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.08,
    "endTime": 496.319,
    "text": "remember to whisk the eggs before adding"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 496.319,
    "endTime": 498.879,
    "text": "the sugar"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.919,
    "endTime": 502.16,
    "text": "remember to turn at the intersection"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 502.16,
    "endTime": 504.479,
    "text": "otherwise you'll get stuck on a one-way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 504.479,
    "endTime": 506.96,
    "text": "road"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 506.96,
    "endTime": 508.08,
    "text": "regret"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.08,
    "endTime": 511.759,
    "text": "the verb regret with a gerund is used to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.759,
    "endTime": 513.518,
    "text": "talk about something that you did in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.519,
    "endTime": 518.0,
    "text": "past that you aren't happy about anymore"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.0,
    "endTime": 519.919,
    "text": "you know decisions that you made in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 519.919,
    "endTime": 521.518,
    "text": "past that you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 521.519,
    "endTime": 524.56,
    "text": "wish you didn't make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.56,
    "endTime": 526.64,
    "text": "when you wish you could go back in time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.64,
    "endTime": 530.32,
    "text": "and change those actions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530.56,
    "endTime": 532.48,
    "text": "he regretted yelling at her as soon as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.48,
    "endTime": 535.519,
    "text": "she walked away"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.519,
    "endTime": 538.32,
    "text": "he woke up with a pounding headache and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.32,
    "endTime": 540.88,
    "text": "immediately regretted drinking so much"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.88,
    "endTime": 542.8,
    "text": "the night before"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.8,
    "endTime": 545.279,
    "text": "what do you wish you could go back in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.279,
    "endTime": 547.2,
    "text": "time and change"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547.2,
    "endTime": 549.44,
    "text": "can you write a sentence about it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 549.44,
    "endTime": 551.36,
    "text": "add it to the comments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.36,
    "endTime": 554.56,
    "text": "now regret with the too infinitive is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.56,
    "endTime": 557.519,
    "text": "used to tell someone bad news or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 557.519,
    "endTime": 560.48,
    "text": "something that they don't want to hear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.48,
    "endTime": 563.12,
    "text": "and this verb pattern is really formal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.12,
    "endTime": 564.16,
    "text": "language"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.16,
    "endTime": 568.64,
    "text": "and it's always followed by bad news"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.64,
    "endTime": 570.56,
    "text": "so these are the words that you don't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.56,
    "endTime": 573.92,
    "text": "want to hear after a job interview"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.92,
    "endTime": 576.08,
    "text": "i regret to say that i wasn't impressed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.08,
    "endTime": 579.04,
    "text": "by the performance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.279,
    "endTime": 581.839,
    "text": "we regret to inform you that you have 10"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.839,
    "endTime": 584.56,
    "text": "days left to pay the account otherwise"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 584.56,
    "endTime": 587.36,
    "text": "we'll close it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.519,
    "endTime": 588.72,
    "text": "mean"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 588.72,
    "endTime": 591.519,
    "text": "we missed our bus which meant waiting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.519,
    "endTime": 594.64,
    "text": "six hours until the next one"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 594.64,
    "endTime": 596.48,
    "text": "did you mean to miss the meeting this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 596.48,
    "endTime": 597.6,
    "text": "morning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597.6,
    "endTime": 600.959,
    "text": "so when mean is followed by a gerund"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.959,
    "endTime": 603.04,
    "text": "it's used to talk about what the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603.04,
    "endTime": 607.76,
    "text": "response or the result of something is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 607.76,
    "endTime": 609.76,
    "text": "make sure you bring your jacket or it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.76,
    "endTime": 614.16,
    "text": "will mean getting really wet and cold"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 614.72,
    "endTime": 616.72,
    "text": "visiting my sister in london means"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.72,
    "endTime": 621.04,
    "text": "spending eight hours on a plane"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.12,
    "endTime": 624.0,
    "text": "mean with the two infinitive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.0,
    "endTime": 627.279,
    "text": "is used when you intend or you plan to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 627.279,
    "endTime": 629.2,
    "text": "do something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 629.2,
    "endTime": 631.92,
    "text": "so when it's used in the past tense this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 631.92,
    "endTime": 636.56,
    "text": "verb is especially useful for excuses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.56,
    "endTime": 639.04,
    "text": "ah i meant to call you last night but i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.04,
    "endTime": 642.079,
    "text": "totally forgot"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642.32,
    "endTime": 644.32,
    "text": "she meant to put sugar in your coffee"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.32,
    "endTime": 647.44,
    "text": "that she accidentally added salt"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.44,
    "endTime": 649.36,
    "text": "so now that you've had plenty of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649.36,
    "endTime": 651.68,
    "text": "practice with gerunds and infinitives"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.68,
    "endTime": 655.04,
    "text": "it's time to move on to a new lesson"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 655.04,
    "endTime": 657.519,
    "text": "don't stop watching yet"
  },
  {
